## Hard constraints

- **Backend = Python standard library only.** No runtime pip deps in the engine.
  Keep **Python 3.9 compatible** (`from __future__ import annotations`; no
  `match`; no `X | Y` runtime unions).
- **One orchestrator:** route new behavior through `packages/borscht/core/engine.py`.
