- **Single state language:** statuses/verdicts/risk live in `core/models.py`.
- **Policies are JSON** packs; fail-closed `deny > require_approval > allow`.
- **UI:** React 18 + Vite + TS (strict). New npm dep â‡’ update `package.json` **and**
